com.skratchdot.riff.wav.impl

Class ChunkInstrumentImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • EObjectImpl
      • com.skratchdot.riff.wav.impl.ChunkImpl
        • com.skratchdot.riff.wav.impl.ChunkInstrumentImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Chunk, ChunkInstrument

    public class ChunkInstrumentImpl
extends ChunkImpl
implements ChunkInstrument
    An implementation of the model object 'Chunk Instrument'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Unshifted Note
    • Fine Tune
    • Gain
    • Low Note
    • High Note
    • Low Velocity
    • High Velocity
